    <span class="marquee-item">30-day money-back guarantee</span>
    <span class="marquee-item">Made in India</span>
    <span class="marquee-item"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M3 13h13l-1.5 4h-7L4 7H1V5h4l3.6 8h6.4l1.4-4H5z"/></svg> FREE shipping on orders over <span class="accent">₹999</span></span>
    <span class="marquee-item">30-day money-back guarantee</span>
