            </div>
          <% } %>
        </form>
        <p class="pi-footnote">Free shipping over ₹999 · 30-day money-back guarantee</p>
        <figure class="pi-benefits">
          <img src="/img/products/iron-benefits.png" alt="Iron+ benefits — boosts hemoglobin gently, reduces pregnancy fatigue, supports fetal brain, one vegecap daily" loading="lazy">
        </figure>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FEATURED READER LETTER — full-bleed editorial pull quote -->
<section class="pi-feature" aria-label="Featured reader letter" style="background:#fff;color:#1A1A1A">
  <div class="wrap">
    <span class="rv-marker" style="color:rgba(26,26,26,0.55)">Featured · Reader Letter 01</span>
    <blockquote class="pi-feature__quote" style="color:#1A1A1A">
      <span class="pi-feature__open" aria-hidden="true" style="color:#E11D48">"</span>
      I came off two iron tablets that left me nauseous and exhausted. My OB suggested Shiōrra Iron+. By week four my energy was back, my Hb was rising, and for the first time in this pregnancy I wasn't dreading the morning capsule.
      <span class="pi-feature__close" aria-hidden="true" style="color:#E11D48">"</span>
    </blockquote>
